data.text: @Martin__Higgins Trump has made America the laughing stock of the world- nothing great about that. He is a bigot, bully and sexist. His supporters worship him as did Hitler’s. It’s sad that anyone supports him- let alone someone who is a member of a race which Trump has shown so much contempt. 🙏🏽

@KatherineEgland I think it’s the way he articulates his speeches that people can pick on him and the fact that he supports trump, but I don’t see why people would disagree with trump unemployment is down across the board, stick market high, Korea dispute at a close end.

@Martin__Higgins According to T.I. Ye has political aspirations. He certainly might feel that gushing over Trump would yield a political appointment to jumpstart his aspiration. He has a right to free speech and to his support of Trump. But his outbursts are the ramblings of a misguided minstrel.
